query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS projectInspirationLinks (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  projectId INT NOT NULL,
  inspirationId INT NOT NULL,
  notes TEXT,
  addedById INT NOT NULL,
  addedAt TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  FOREIGN KEY (projectId) REFERENCES projects(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  FOREIGN KEY (inspirationId) REFERENCES libraryInspiration(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  FOREIGN KEY (addedById) REFERENCES users(id),
  INDEX projectInspiration_project_idx (projectId),
  INDEX projectInspiration_inspiration_idx (inspirationId)
);
